rows.label: tlk45300071_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Just take a look at this view!
Isn't it spectacular? You can see
the head of Acedia so clearly!

rows.label: tlk45300071_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Standing here, I feel almost like I've
become a bird, gliding across the
wide Cloud Sea below.

rows.label: tlk45300071_01_msg0003
rows.name:
You should try this too sometime, you
know - find a high point that juts out,
and toss some money into the clouds.

rows.label: tlk45300071_01_msg0004
rows.name:
They say if you throw money into the
Cloud Sea from high above, your wish
will come true! I sure hope mine does.
